MpH.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1505,"height":847,"file_path":"/7YI8UEQqe1P3qU3e2Kn4SQPRHS1.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1660,"height":934,"file_path":"/lP9W4nY46YbGZN2jYZ6RnSYqjeS.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/ns8CTFkDruTAzp03vGvJsPewQBy.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1637,"height":921,"file_path":"/jWhn3JXY6FbejovjyzHf7kSOIVz.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1557,"height":876,"file_path":"/h3ELuC4QAICuDSHLlaKIdezIooT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1648,"height":927,"file_path":"/sufevytumodK7ThKG4glgn7Nau1.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1636,"height":920,"file_path":"/j264yWJhDJdCb2MFTw0KiBFqEQj.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1445,"height":813,"file_path":"/kf9PqsWkhMJBBFXHzWShUnbVMur.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1644,"height":925,"file_path":"/56tPBTM536lclsAX6nsa2tj3jVw.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/tuYTJOQsfETgYTB5J9cwta3nrsC.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/7ozXgW22MaFVoGqdD69AKEHeVfI.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/oqWESiWK2QqRQid0nEV8Cy3NyhH.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/cSRirhKn3QPs3oUezioaM5EES7T.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T11:55:34.535+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"JUJUTSU KAISEN: Hidden Inventory / Premature Death - The Movie","runtime":110,"tagline":"The bond of the strongest duo, a time they lost forever...","homepage":"https://gkids.com/films/jujutsu-kaisen-hidden-inventory-premature-death-the-movie","overview":"Pursued by a religious cult and other curse users, former friends Satoru Gojo and Suguru Geto are the only sorcerers capable of carrying the difficult task of protecting Riko Amanai, a student who has been designated to be sacrificed as the Star Plasma Vessel, until she can fulfill her duty."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"最強の2人の、もう戻れない青い春—","homepage":"https://jujutsukaisen.jp/kaigyokugyokusetsu/","overview":"2018年6月、両面宿儺を己の身に宿した虎杖悠仁。2017年12月、祈本里香の呪いを解いた乙骨憂太。そして更に時は遡り2006年（春）—。高専時代の五条 悟と夏油 傑。呪術師として活躍し、向かうところ敵のない2人の元に、不死の術式を持つ呪術界の要・天元からの依頼が届く。依頼は2つ。天元との適合者である“星漿体” 天内理子、その少女の「護衛」と「抹消」。呪術界存続の為の護衛任務へと赴くことになった2人だが、そこに伏黒を名乗る“術師殺し”が“星漿体”の暗殺を狙い介入する…。後に最強の呪術師と最悪の呪詛師と呼ばれる五条と夏油、道を違えた2人の過去が明かされる―。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"JUJUTSU KAISEN: Hidden Inventory / Premature Death - The Movie","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Gojo e Geto devem proteger Riko Amanai, marcada como o sacrifício do Star Plasma Vessel. Caçados por cultistas e usuários de maldições, esses poderosos feiticeiros enfrentam uma missão que testará seus limites e moldará seu futuro"},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Chú Thuật Hồi Chiến: Hoài Ngọc / Ngọc Chiết - The Movie","runtime":0,"tagline":"“Tôi không thể ở bên các bạn được nữa”","homepage":"https://jujutsukaisen.jp/","overview":"PHIM ĐIỆN ẢNH | CHÚ THUẬT HỒI CHIẾN - HỒI NGỌC: NGỌC TOÁI  Phần này tiếp tục phần truyện mùa II sẽ có hai phần. Phần này sẽ về Hồi Ngọc: Ngọc Toái."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Theatrale compilatie van de eerste boog van seizoen 2."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Hidden Inventory / Premature Death - The Movie","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bevor sie zu Feinden wurden, waren Satoru Gojo und Suguru Geto Klassenkameraden und Freunde. Die beiden werden mit dem Schutz Riko Amanais beauftragt, einer Schülerin, die als Sternplasmahülle geopfert werden soll, bis sie in der Lage ist, ihre Pflicht zu erfüllen. Mit einem religiösen Kult und anderen Fluchmagiern sind nur die beiden dazu imstande. Doch diese Mission wird ihr Schicksal verändern und die beiden Jujuzisten in unvorstellbarem Maße auf die Probe stellen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"咒术回战 怀玉·玉折 总集篇","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"劇場版 咒術迴戰 懷玉．玉折","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"「最強的 2 人 一去不返的青春」 那段圍繞著詛咒，不容錯過的故事將於大銀幕再次展開 最強的 2 人 回不去的青春 2018 年 6 月，虎杖悠仁讓兩面宿儺寄宿於自身體內。\r 2017 年 12 月，乙骨憂太解開了祈本里香的詛咒。\r 而時光一路回溯至 2006 年的春天。高專時代的五條悟與夏油傑。\r 兩人是表現活躍的咒術師，所向無敵，接到來自擁有不死術式的咒術界重鎮──天元的委託。\r 委託有兩項。針對天元的適合者「星漿體」天內理子，擔任那名少女「護衞」並且「抹消」。\r 為了使咒術界永存，兩人前往執行護衞任務，卻在這時有一名自稱是伏黑的「術師殺手」介入，企圖暗殺「星漿體」…… 日後成為最強咒術師與最兇惡咒詛師的五條與夏油，分道揚鑣的兩人的過去即將揭曉……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"劇場版 咒術迴戰 懷玉‧玉折","runtime":0,"tagline":"最強的兩人，無法回頭的青春","homepage":"","overview":"故事設定在2006年，二年級生的五條悟與夏油傑奉命保護一位名為天內理子的少女，她體內的「星漿體」讓她背負每500年與天元大人同化的宿命，藉以維持咒術界的恆久穩定，任務中，自信滿滿的兩人遭遇殺手伏黑慎爾的伏擊，伏黑慎爾不僅威脅了護衛任務的執行，更徹底顛覆兩人的信念與命運，讓兩人從此走上不同的道路。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"JUJUTSU KAISEN: Hidden Inventory / Premature Death - The Movie","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Perseguidos por una secta religiosa y otros usuarios de maldiciones, compañeros hechos enemigos Satoru Gojo y Suguru Geto son los únicos hechiceros capaces de proteger a Riko Amanai, una estudiante que ha sido designada para ser sacrificada como Recipiente de Plasma Estelar hasta que pueda cumplir con su deber, pero esta misión marcará sus destinos y desafiará a los dos hechiceros de formas inimaginables."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Магическая битва: Пагубный талант / Таланты умирают молодыми","runtime":111,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"","iso_639_1":"co","iso_3166_1":"CO","english_name":"Corsican"},{"data":{"title":"JUJUTSU KAISEN : Trésor caché / Mort prématurée – Le Film","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Avant d'être ennemis, Satoru Gojo et Suguru Geto étaient camarades de classe et amis au lycée. Les deux puissants exorcistes sont chargés de protéger Riko Amanai, une étudiante qui a été désignée pour être sacrifiée en tant que Réceptacle du Plasma stellaire, jusqu'à ce qu'elle puisse accomplir son devoir. Poursuivis par une secte religieuse et d'autres maîtres des fléaux, ils sont les seuls exorcistes capables de mener à bien une mission si difficile – mais cette mission scellera leurs destins et mettra les deux exorcistes à l'épreuve de manière inimaginable."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"JUJUTSU KAISEN: El tesoro escondido / El tesoro perdido - La película","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร เดอะมูฟวี: พรสวรรค์เร้น • อกาลมรณะ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ก่อนที่พวกเขาจะกลายมาเป็นศัตรูกัน โกะโจ ซาโตรุ และ เกะโท สุงุรุ เคยเป็นเพื่อนนักเรียนมัธยมปลายกันมาก่อน สองผู้ใช้คุณไสยที่แข็งแกร่งที่สุดได้ถูกมอบหมายหน้าที่ให้ปกป้อง ริโกะ อามานาอิ นักเรียนผู้ถูกขีดชะตาเอาไว้ให้เป็นเครื่องสังเวยในฐานะของ เซโชโท จนกว่าเธอจะสามารถทำหน้าที่ของเธอได้ โดยพวกเขาจะถูกตามล่าโดยพวกคลั่งศาสนาและผู้ใช้คุณไสยคนอื่น ๆ ทำให้ทั้งสองคน เป็นเพียงคุณไสยที่จะสามารถทำภารกิจที่โหดหินนี้ไปได้ แต่ภารกิจนี้ จะขีดเส้นชะตา และท้าทายสองผู้ใช้คุณไสยที่แบบที่ยากจะจินตนาการถึง"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"JUJUTSU KAISEN: Hidden Inventory / Premature Death – The Movie","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Prima che diventassero nemici, Satoru Gojo e Suguru Geto erano compagni di classe e amici. A questi due potenti stregoni viene affidato il compito di proteggere Riko Amanai, una studentessa destinata a diventare il Ventre del Fluido Astrale, fino al giorno in cui dovrà compiere il suo dovere. Con una setta religiosa e degli stregoni neri alle calcagna, Gojo e Geto sono gli unici in grado di portare a termine un compito così arduo, ma questa missione segnerà i loro destini e li metterà alla prova in modi inimmaginabili."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"극장판 주술회전: 회옥·옥절","runtime":111,"tagline":"최강의 두 사람 이제는 돌아갈 수 없는 푸르른 봄","homepage":"","overview":"최강의 두 사람, 다시는 돌아갈 수 없는 푸른 봄. 2006년 봄, 주술고등전문학교 시절의 고죠 사토루와 게토 스구루. 불사의 술식을 가진 주술계 핵심, 텐겐으로부터 의뢰가 도착한다. 의뢰는 두 가지, 텐겐과 적합자인 성장체 아마나이 리코라는 소녀의 ‘호위’와 ‘말소’. 두 사람은 주술계 존속을 위한 호위 임무에 나서지만 후시구로라 불리는 ‘주술사 킬러’가 암살을 노리고 나타난다. 최강의 주술사와 최악의 주저사가 된 고죠와 게토, 두 사람의 엇갈린 운명의 과거가 밝혀진다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"جوجوتسو کایسن: گذشته پنهان / مرگ نابهنگام","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"دوست های سابق، گوجو و گتو باید از ریکو آمانای محافظت کنند، دختری که برای قربانی شدن برگزیده شده است..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"ג'וג'וטסו קאיזן הסרט: מלאי סודי / מוות בטרם עת","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1355666,"adult":false,"title":"Love Untangled","video":false,"overview":"A lovestruck teen plans to win the school heartthrob by going from curly to straight hair — until a new transfer student changes everything.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3337,"vote_count":164,"poster_path":"/e7jStO2xfBUAUK37LbINHd1qtgy.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-28","vote_average":8.369,"backdrop_path":"/oBcvmHD7lbaX8RZ7NXvO05fIJef.jpg","original_title":"고백의 역사","original_language":"ko"},{"id":639988,"adult":false,"title":"No Other Choice","video":false,"overview":"After being laid off and humiliated by a ruthless job market, a veteran paper mill manager descends into violence in a desperate bid to reclaim his dignity.","genre_ids":[80,53,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":37.402,"vote_count":699,"poster_path":"/sBpxTGLzKnvPSVtL5yQYpSxvKEb.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-24","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/s6aB9kjxNg0mu2361IkCUSpyHJV.jpg","original_title":"어쩔수가없다","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1372489,"adult":false,"title":"Doraemon the Movie: Nobita's Art World Tales","video":true,"overview":"44th film in the Doraemon the Movie series  The story is set in the magnificent medieval European world depicted in the pictures. Doraemon and his friends dive into the 'world of pictures' and have a great adventure in this completely original story!!","genre_ids":[12,16,10751,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.4348,"vote_count":35,"poster_path":"/tf7NQJ4zL8iCN1aPi8Q5HHyeWSO.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-07","vote_average":7.914,"backdrop_path":"/vncMpsAUDnL1JOb73e5q48gX32S.jpg","original_title":"映画ドラえもん のび太の絵世界物語","original_language":"ja"},{"id":810693,"adult":false,"title":"Jujutsu Kaisen 0","video":false,"overview":"Yuta Okkotsu is a nervous high school student who is suffering from a serious problem—his childhood friend Rika has turned into a curse and won't leave him alone. Since Rika is no ordinary curse, his plight is noticed by Satoru Gojo, a teacher at Jujutsu High, a school where fledgling exorcists learn how to combat curses. Gojo convinces Yuta to enroll, but can he learn enough in time to confront the curse that haunts him?","genre_ids":[16,28,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.3532,"vote_count":1660,"poster_path":"/23oJaeBh0FDk2mQ2P240PU9Xxfh.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-24","vote_average":8.118,"backdrop_path":"/rcEDPOOOUTLFxLLQJggfLffbofe.jpg","original_title":"劇場版 呪術廻戦 0","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1061474,"adult":false,"title":"Superman","video":false,"overview":"Superman, a journalist in Metropolis, embarks on a journey to reconcile his Kryptonian heritage with his human upbringing as Clark Kent.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":30.5535,"vote_count":4344,"poster_path":"/oe5TVF6GQDESLsGiFrN6GyJEekh.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-09","vote_average":7.368,"backdrop_path":"/aJDLz1748CIMZkCkyISYe5Hl6I7.jpg","original_title":"Superman","original_language":"en"},{"id":1933,"adult":false,"title":"The Others","video":false,"overview":"Grace is a religious woman who lives in an old house kept dark because her two children, Anne and Nicholas, have a rare sensitivity to light. When the family begins to suspect the house is haunted, Grace fights to protect her children at any cost in the face of strange events and disturbing visions.","genre_ids":[27,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.2666,"vote_count":7012,"poster_path":"/p8g1vlTvpM6nr2hMMiZ1fUlKF0D.jpg","release_date":"2001-08-02","vote_average":7.617,"backdrop_path":"/rbBe9WQ1OqCxzgwskOTnaY6JdUA.jpg","original_title":"The Others","original_language":"en"},{"id":378064,"adult":false,"title":"A Silent Voice: The Movie","video":false,"overview":"Shouya Ishida starts bullying the new girl in class, Shouko Nishimiya, because she is deaf. But as the teasing continues, the rest of the class starts to turn on Shouya for his lack of compassion. When they leave elementary school, Shouko and Shouya do not speak to each other again... until an older, wiser Shouya, tormented by his past behaviour, decides he must see Shouko once more. He wants to atone for his sins, but is it already too late...?","genre_ids":[16,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.3838,"vote_count":4364,"poster_path":"/tuFaWiqX0TXoWu7DGNcmX3UW7sT.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-17","vote_average":8.383,"backdrop_path":"/5lAMQMWpXMsirvtLLvW7cJgEPkU.jpg","original_title":"映画 聲の形","original_language":"ja"},{"id":426063,"adult":false,"title":"Nosferatu","video":false,"overview":"A gothic tale of obsession between a haunted young woman and the terrifying vampire infatuated with her, causing untold horror in its wake.","genre_ids":[27,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.944,"vote_count":3451,"poster_path":"/5qGIxdEO841C0tdY8vOdLoRVrr0.jpg","release_date":"2024-12-25","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/fYnEbgoNCxW9kL0IgOgtJb9JTBU.jpg","original_title":"Nosferatu","original_language":"en"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":29.5562,"vote_count":26800,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":10681,"adult":false,"title":"WALL·E","video":false,"overview":"After hundreds of years doing what he was built for, WALL•E— a robot designed to clean up the earth—discovers a new purpose in life when he meets a sleek search robot named EVE. EVE comes to realize that WALL•E has inadvertently stumbled upon the key to the planet's future, and races back to space to report to the humans. Meanwhile, WALL•E chases EVE across the galaxy and sets into motion one of the most imaginative adventures ever brought to the big screen.","genre_ids":[16,10751,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.9035,"vote_count":19934,"poster_path":"/hbhFnRzzg6ZDmm8YAmxBnQpQIPh.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-22","vote_average":8.108,"backdrop_path":"/fK5ssgvtI43z19FoWigdlqgpLRE.jpg","original_title":"WALL·E","original_language":"en"},{"id":150540,"adult":false,"title":"Inside Out","video":false,"overview":"When 11-year-old Riley moves to a new city, her Emotions team up to help her through the transition. Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness work together, but when Joy and Sadness get lost, they must journey through unfamiliar places to get back home.","genre_ids":[16,10751,12,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.8246,"vote_count":23174,"poster_path":"/2H1TmgdfNtsKlU9jKdeNyYL5y8T.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-17","vote_average":7.909,"backdrop_path":"/jJKZaTBNenlFclQyjrnvzkRmvWE.jpg","original_title":"Inside Out","original_language":"en"},{"id":466272,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","video":false,"overview":"Los Angeles, 1969. TV star Rick Dalton, a struggling actor specializing in westerns, and stuntman Cliff Booth, his best friend, try to survive in a constantly changing movie industry. Dalton is the neighbor of the young and promising actress and model Sharon Tate, who has just married the prestigious Polish director Roman Polanski…","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.5698,"vote_count":14559,"poster_path":"/8j58iEBw9pOXFD2L0nt0ZXeHviB.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-24","vote_average":7.424,"backdrop_path":"/kKTPv9LKKs5L3oO1y5FNObxAPWI.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","original_language":"en"},{"id":37165,"adult":false,"title":"The Truman Show","video":false,"overview":"An insurance salesman begins to suspect that his whole life is actually some sort of reality TV show.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.1631,"vote_count":19811,"poster_path":"/vuza0WqY239yBXOadKlGwJsZJFE.jpg","release_date":"1998-06-04","vote_average":8.151,"backdrop_path":"/aCHn2TXYJfzPXQKA6r9mKPbMlUB.jpg","original_title":"The Truman Show","original_language":"en"},{"id":680,"adult":false,"title":"Pulp Fiction","video":false,"overview":"A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster's moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.","genre_ids":[53,80,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":23.9216,"vote_count":29708,"poster_path":"/vQWk5YBFWF4bZaofAbv0tShwBvQ.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-10","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/96hiUXEuYsu4tcnvlaY8tEMFM0m.jpg","original_title":"Pulp Fiction","original_language":"en"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":20.7457,"vote_count":27317,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":272,"adult":false,"title":"Batman Begins","video":false,"overview":"Driven by tragedy, billionaire Bruce Wayne dedicates his life to uncovering and defeating the corruption that plagues his home, Gotham City.  Unable to work within the system, he instead creates a new identity, a symbol of fear for the criminal underworld - The 