 mysterious systems failure causes the crew of a spaceship to be stranded on the dark side of the moon, while rapidly running out of fuel and oxygen. They are surprised to discover a NASA space shuttle floating in space, and board it in the hope of salvaging some supplies. One by one, the crew is possessed and killed, and it is up to Paxton Warner to find the links between the dark side of the moon, the Bermuda Triangle, and the Devil himself.","genre_ids":[27,28,53,878],"popularity":0.4269,"vote_count":90,"poster_path":"/etnsPUDbgbMGna2hiuRvHDx0xyz.jpg","release_date":"1990-05-30","vote_average":4.967,"backdrop_path":"/tPVphtpJtuHTC7vLsc71R0DmTLr.jpg","original_title":"The Dark Side of the Moon","original_language":"en"},{"id":249287,"adult":false,"title":"Zillion: Burning Night","video":false,"overview":"In the 24th century, on the war-torn planet Maris the conniving Queen Adama abducts Apple, a member of an heroic trio known as the White Knights, and imprisons her in the infamous Zone. Even though no one has ever returned alive from the Zone — and despite the low ammo at their disposal — the other knights follow their companion. What they find there, however, is an enigmatic figure with a mind-bending revelation...","genre_ids":[16,12,878],"popularity":0.4353,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/bV4l7hbYU6kwreyLQaIvmbzeh6C.jpg","release_date":"1988-06-21","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/Ar0z41ErRQF9JqBG2LYyj8zXujX.jpg","original_title":"赤い光弾ジリオン 歌姫夜曲","original_language":"ja"},{"id":823,"adult":false,"title":"Jin-Roh: The Wolf Brigade","video":false,"overview":"A member of an elite paramilitary counter-terrorism unit becomes traumatized after witnessing the suicide bombing of a young girl and is forced to undergo retraining. However, unbeknownst to him, he becomes a key player in a dispute between rival police divisions, as he finds himself increasingly involved with the sister of the girl he saw die.","genre_ids":[16,18,10749,53,878],"popularity":2.1022,"vote_cou